                        <interp inst="t18390812-name-454" type="given" value="JACOB"></interp>JACOB CROWTHER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a police-constable of Isleworth. The pri<lb></lb>soners were given to me—I asked Nias if he took the fruit, he said, "Yes,"—I asked Hester why he took it—he said he wanted a little, and he only took two pottles.</p>
